# VirtualPartner local ASR generated artifacts
VirtualPartner/LocalServices/ASR/.venv/
VirtualPartner/LocalServices/ASR/__pycache__/
VirtualPartner/LocalServices/ASR/models/
VirtualPartner/LocalServices/ASR/logs/
VirtualPartner/LocalServices/ASR/tmp/
